Courtesy of #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - President Cyril Ramaphosa says the ANC NEC will meet with Bathabile Dlamini. Two weeks ago the Johannesburg Magistrates Court found her guilty of perjury after she lied under oath during an inquiry into the SASSA social grants debacle. WATCH: Bathabile Dlamini found guilty of perjury Ramaphosa said, "the decision on the NEC was that the officials will meet with Bathabile [Dlamini]. That is a process, we going to meet with her we going to have discussions." "We are process driven and we are going to meet her and have discussions with her.”